import { Grid } from '@mui/material'
import { Container } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const BrewingChange = () => {
  return (
    <Container mt={8}>
    <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={4}>
            image
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
            text
        </Grid>
    </Grid>



    </Container>
  )
}

export default BrewingChange
